data.description: Sitting on a corner lot, this three bedroom, one bath home offers main floor living at a reasonable price. The home boasts a metal roof, vinyl siding, and a newer HVAC system. The eat-in kitchen offers great space for meal prep and a newer stove and refrigerator that will stay with the home. The large back yard provides ample space for outdoor activities. Be sure to check this home out. At this price tag, it won't last long!
